<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">等不等觀雜錄</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">「讀法華經妙音品」等</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">送日本得大上人之武林</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
