<lb ed="B" n="0612b11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="17"><cb:jhead>等不等觀雜錄卷二</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b12"/><byline cb:type="author">清石埭楊文會仁山箸</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b13"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pB28p0612b1301">佛學書目表</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b14"/><table cols="5"><row><cell>書名</cell><cell>箸者譯者</cell><cell>卷數</cell><cell>刻版處</cell><cell>識語</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0612b15"/>華嚴部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b16"/>華嚴經</cell><cell>唐實义難陀譯</cell><cell>八十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>佛初成道時。七處九會。說圓融無盡法門。為諸經之王。非閱疏論著述。鮮能通其義也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0612b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0613a" n="0613a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a01"/>華嚴懸談</cell><cell>唐澄觀撰</cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>長沙上林寺</cell><cell>懸敘十門。統明全經大旨。即疏鈔之首。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a04"/>華嚴疏鈔</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>二百二十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>以四分科經。發揮精詳。後人得通華嚴奧旨者。賴有此書也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a08"/>華嚴合論</cell><cell>唐李通玄撰</cell><cell>一百二十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>提倡圓頓法門。與禪相為表裏。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a10"/>華嚴著述集要</cell><cell>刻經處輯</cell><cell></cell><cell>同</cell><cell>薈萃各家撰述。學華嚴者。萬不可少。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0613a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a12"/>方等部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a13"/>圓覺經近釋</cell><cell>唐佛陀多羅譯<p xml:id="pB28p0613a1312" cb:place="inline">明通潤釋</p></cell><cell>六卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>十二菩薩。各別請問。佛一一答之。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a16"/>維摩經註</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯<p xml:id="pB28p0613a1612" cb:place="inline">僧肇註</p></cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>維摩示疾。諸大菩薩往問。說不可思議解脫法門。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a19"/>金光明最勝玉經</cell><cell>唐義淨譯</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>四卷金光明經廣行於世。此十卷者。文義詳備。最宜流通。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0613b" n="0613b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b03"/>心地觀經</cell><cell>唐般若譯</cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>純顯真如一心。兼明萬行修證。文言流暢。旨趣幽深。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b06"/>勝鬘經寶窟</cell><cell>劉宋求那跋陀羅譯<p xml:id="pB28p0613b0614" cb:place="inline">唐吉藏作寶窟</p></cell><cell>十五卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>唐以前盛弘此經。後世無人提倡。因其奧義難通也。今幸寶窟來自扶桑。學者可得門徑矣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b11"/>思益梵天所問經</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>學禪宗者。宜閱此經。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b13"/>觀佛三昧海經</cell><cell>東晉佛陀跋陀羅譯</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此經事理交含。依文修觀。現身得見釋迦如來。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b16"/>佛報恩經</cell><cell>失譯人名出後漢錄</cell><cell>七卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>如來往劫修行。皆是證無生忍以後之事。非凡情所能測度。其中表法。可以理喻。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0613b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0614a" n="0614a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a01"/>地藏本願經</cell><cell>唐實义難陀譯</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>說地藏菩薩因地發心。併地獄可畏之相。以儆愚頑。而開覺路。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0614a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a05"/>淨土部<note place="inline">方等部內開出</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a07"/>無量壽經義疏</cell><cell>曹魏康僧鎧譯<p xml:id="pB28p0614a0713" cb:place="inline">隋慧遠疏</p></cell><cell>六卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>說彌陀因地發四十八願莊嚴淨土。此疏從日本傳來。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a10"/>觀無量壽佛經疏鈔</cell><cell>劉宋畺良耶舍譯<p xml:id="pB28p0614a1016" cb:place="inline">陳隋智顗疏宋知禮鈔</p></cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>佛說十六觀門。利根上智。依之修行。速超上品。疏鈔用三觀釋之。顯圓妙理。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a15"/>觀無量壽佛經四帖疏</cell><cell>唐善導疏</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>從日本傳來。內分玄義分。序分義。定善義。散善義。故名四帖</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a19"/>阿彌陀經義疏</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯<p xml:id="pB28p0614a1914" cb:place="inline">宋元照疏</p></cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>佛說淨土法門。令眾生一心念佛。即得往生。不受輪轉。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0614b" n="0614b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b02"/>阿彌陀經疏鈔</cell><cell>明袾宏撰</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>用賢首家法一事一理。逗機正說。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b04"/>往生論註</cell><cell>婆藪槃頭菩薩造論<p xml:id="pB28p0614b0413" cb:place="inline">元魏菩提留支譯</p><p xml:id="pB28p0614b0420" cb:place="inline">魏曇鸞註</p></cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>唐以前談淨土之書。除十疑論外。僅見此本。其精妙處。後人所不能及。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b09"/>淨土十要</cell><cell>明智旭集</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>上起智者。下至袁宏道。皆係精要之作。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b12"/>往生集</cell><cell>明袾宏輯</cell><cell>三卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>略錄古今往生事蹟。加以讚論。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b14"/>省庵語錄</cell><cell>國朝實賢作</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>專弘淨土。時人稱為蓮宗第九祖。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0614b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b16"/>法相部<note place="inline">方等部內開出</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b18"/>楞伽經</cell><cell>劉宋求那跋陀羅譯</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>性相並談。文義簡古。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0614b20"/>入楞伽心玄義</cell><cell>唐法藏撰</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此卷從日本得來。全疏既失。觀此可知大意。</cell></row><row><cell>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0615a" n="0615a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a03"/>解深密經</cell><cell>唐玄奘譯</cell><cell>五卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>學法相者。以此為宗。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a05"/>大乘密嚴經</cell><cell>唐大廣智不空譯</cell><cell>三卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>長行甚少。五言偈居多。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a07"/>瑜伽師地論</cell><cell>彌勒菩薩說<p xml:id="pB28p0615a0711" cb:place="inline">無著菩薩傳</p><p xml:id="pB28p0615a0716" cb:place="inline">唐玄奘譯</p></cell><cell>百卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>內有五分說十七地。奘師譯成。太宗大為讚賞。因作聖教序。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a11"/>成唯識論</cell><cell>護法等菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0615a1111" cb:place="inline">唐玄奘譯</p></cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>梵本十種。奘公會為一部。剖析精微。學法相者。最宜深究。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a15"/>成唯識論述記</cell><cell>唐窺基撰</cell><cell>六十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此書元末失傳。後人以不見為憾。今從日本得來。慈恩一宗。其再興乎。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a19"/>因明論疏</cell><cell>商羯羅主菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0615a1912" cb:place="inline">唐玄奘譯</p><p xml:id="pB28p0615a1916" cb:place="inline">唐窺基疏</p></cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>用三支比量。簡辨真似。能立能破。不為他宗所破也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0615b" n="0615b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b03"/>相宗八要解</cell><cell>明明昱解</cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>雪浪恩公採集。明昱補古註所未備。開相宗之初門。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0615b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b06"/>般若部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b07"/>金剛經註解</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯<p xml:id="pB28p0615b0713" cb:place="inline">明宗泐解</p></cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>宗天親二十七疑解釋。最便初學。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b10"/>金剛宗通</cell><cell>明曾鳳儀撰</cell><cell>九卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>引證淵博。會通宗旨。文義暢達。震醒聾瞶。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b13"/>心經五家註</cell><cell>唐靖邁　法藏<p xml:id="pB28p0615b1311" cb:place="inline">明宗泐　德清　智旭撰</p></cell><cell>五卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此經註解甚多。俗解無益。邪解有害。擇正解之精當者。彙為一編。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b18"/>仁王護國經</cell><cell>唐大廣智不空譯</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>波斯匿王請問。佛說般若護國法門。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0615b20"/>六波羅密多經</cell><cell>唐般若譯</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>前五度一一與般若相應。方成無漏善也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0616a" n="0616a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a03"/>大智度論</cell><cell>龍樹菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0616a0310" cb:place="inline">姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</p></cell><cell>百卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>釋摩訶般若經九十品。初品具譯全釋有三十四卷。餘皆十倍略之。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0616a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a07"/>法華部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a08"/>妙法蓮華經</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</cell><cell>七卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>開權顯實。統收一代時教。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a10"/>法華會義</cell><cell>明智旭撰</cell><cell>十六卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>智者大師法華文句。文義繁多。閱者每難卒業。智旭刪繁就簡。以便初學。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a14"/>妙玄節要</cell><cell>明智旭節</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>節略智者大師法華玄義而成此本。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a16"/>尼犍子授記經</cell><cell>元魏菩提留支譯</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>宣說世出世法。曲盡其妙。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0616a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a18"/>涅槃部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a19"/>大般涅槃經</cell><cell>北涼曇無讖譯<p xml:id="pB28p0616a1912" cb:place="inline">後分唐若那跋陀羅等譯</p></cell><cell>四十二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>扶律談常。顯佛不滅。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0616b" n="0616b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b04"/>涅槃玄義</cell><cell>隋灌頂撰</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>開為五重。統說全經大意。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b06"/>集一切福德三昧經</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</cell><cell>三卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>受持此經。令三寶種永不斷絕。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b08"/>佛遺教經節要</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯<p xml:id="pB28p0616b0814" cb:place="inline">宋淨源節要</p><p xml:id="pB28p0616b0819" cb:place="inline">明袾宏補註</p></cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>佛說此經。猶後世之遺囑。後代學人。皆宜遵守。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0616b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b13"/>祕密部</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b14"/>楞嚴經</cell><cell>唐般<note n="0616b1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">剌【CB】，刺【補編】</note><app n="0616b1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">剌</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">刺</rdg></app>密帝譯</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>無法不備。無機不攝。學佛之要門也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b16"/>楞嚴正脈</cell><cell>明交光撰</cell><cell>四十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>披剝陳言。獨申正見。發揮經義。超越古今。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b19"/>準提陀羅尼經</cell><cell>唐金剛智譯</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>治病卻魔。祈福修真。四種神呪。隨宜</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0616b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0617a" n="0617a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a01"/>大悲陀羅尼經</cell><cell>唐伽梵達摩譯</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>奉持。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a03"/>尊勝陀羅尼經</cell><cell>唐佛陀波利譯</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a05"/>穢迹金剛呪經</cell><cell>唐無能勝譯</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a07"/>顯密圓通</cell><cell>宋道<g ref="#CB01324"/>集</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>略明顯教。廣明密教。以準提為宗。欲知呪術功能。須閱此集。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a11"/>施食<note place="inline">儀軌補註</note></cell><cell>明袾宏述</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>三業相應。力用無邊。閱此補註方知施食非易事也。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0617a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a14"/>阿含部<note place="inline">小乘經</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a16"/>增壹阿含經</cell><cell>符秦曇摩難提譯</cell><cell>五十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>此經明人天因果。從一增一。義豐慧廣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a19"/>長阿含經</cell><cell>姚秦佛陀耶舍共竺佛念譯</cell><cell>二十二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>辨邪正。明報應。以長為目者。開斥修途。所記長遠也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0617b" n="0617b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b02"/>雜阿含經</cell><cell>劉宋求那跋陀羅譯</cell><cell>五十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>此經說事既雜。別為一部。內有小半與中阿含。增壹阿含相同。而文順暢。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0617b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b06"/>大乘律<note place="inline">小乘律專為出家者設故不載</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b09"/>梵網經</cell><cell>姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>上卷說四十心地。下卷說十重四十八輕戒。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b12"/>梵網經菩薩戒疏</cell><cell>唐法藏撰</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此疏從日本傳來。學菩薩道者。最宜深究。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b15"/>菩薩戒本經箋要</cell><cell>北涼曇無讖譯<p xml:id="pB28p0617b1514" cb:place="inline">明智旭箋</p></cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>廣明開遮持犯。在家出家。均宜受持。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0617b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b18"/>大乘論<note place="inline">小乘論未刻</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b20"/>大乘起信論義記</cell><cell>馬鳴菩薩造論<p xml:id="pB28p0617b2014" cb:place="inline">梁真諦譯</p><p xml:id="pB28p0617b2018" cb:place="inline">唐法藏記</p></cell><cell>七卷<p xml:id="pB28p0617b2024" cb:place="inline">附別記一卷</p></cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>此論總括羣經要義。法藏作記。曲盡其妙。學者熟讀深思。自能通達三藏教海。</cell></row><row><cell>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0618a" n="0618a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a05"/>大乘起信論纂註</cell><cell>明真界註</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>取賢首疏長水筆削記。刪繁就簡。纂輯成文。以便初學。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a08"/>大乘起信論直解</cell><cell>明德清解</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>稱性直談。雅合禪門之機。以上二種。可作義記先導</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a11"/>中論</cell><cell>龍樹菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0618a1108" cb:place="inline">青目菩薩釋</p><p xml:id="pB28p0618a1113" cb:place="inline">姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</p></cell><cell>六卷</cell><cell>杭州慧空經房</cell><cell>中論。百論。十二門論。六朝僧專門學習。是為三論宗。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a16"/>般若燈論</cell><cell>龍樹菩薩偈本<p xml:id="pB28p0618a1611" cb:place="inline">分別明菩薩釋論</p><p xml:id="pB28p0618a1618" cb:place="inline">唐波羅頗密多羅譯</p></cell><cell>十五卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>般若明燈。照破幽暗。顯真空理。當處無生。凡夫與佛。平等一如。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0618b" n="0618b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b02"/>十二門論宗致義記</cell><cell>龍樹菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0618b0214" cb:place="inline">姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</p><p xml:id="pB28p0618b0221" cb:place="inline">唐法藏記</p></cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此論意旨。即孔子所云空空如也。我叩其兩端而竭焉。法藏義記。發揮盡致。於此會得。即入三空解脫門。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b08"/>法界無差別論疏</cell><cell>堅慧菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0618b0813" cb:place="inline">唐提雲般若等譯</p><p xml:id="pB28p0618b0820" cb:place="inline">唐法藏疏</p></cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>論中深義。人不能曉。得法藏疏。方知法界平等之妙旨也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b13"/>發菩提心論</cell><cell>天親菩薩造<p xml:id="pB28p0618b1311" cb:place="inline">姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</p></cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>非菩提心。無由作佛。慨發大心。兼行六度。而後佛果可期矣。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0618b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b17"/>西土撰集</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b18"/>四十二章經解</cell><cell>後漢迦葉摩騰竺法蘭同譯<p xml:id="pB28p0618b1818" cb:place="inline">明智旭解</p></cell><cell>三經合本</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>佛教東來。首譯此經。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0619a" n="0619a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a02"/>賢愚因緣經</cell><cell>元魏慧覺譯</cell><cell>十三卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>慧覺等八人。在于闐大會。共記所聞。集為一部。皆係佛及弟子化度眾生之事。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a07"/>諸經要集</cell><cell>唐智嚴譯</cell><cell>三卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>集諸經中菩薩行門六十六條。法珠之寶聚。大乘之<g ref="#CB07632"/>鑑。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a11"/>坐禪三昧經</cell><cell>僧伽羅剎造<p xml:id="pB28p0619a1111" cb:place="inline">姚秦鳩摩羅什譯</p></cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>說五種觀門。以治五障。併說四禪四空念佛等法。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0619a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a15"/>禪宗<note place="inline">以下支那撰述</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a17"/>御選語錄</cell><cell>雍正朝梓行</cell><cell>十九卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>自肇公至蓮池凡十六家。繼以歷代禪師。前後二集。以當今法會為殿。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0619b" n="0619b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b01"/>指月錄</cell><cell>明瞿汝稷集</cell><cell>三十二卷</cell><cell>杭州慧空經房</cell><cell>上起七佛。下至大慧。採集偈頌普說機鋒語句。成一家言。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b05"/>續指月錄</cell><cell>國朝聶先集</cell><cell>二十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>起自南宋。訖於國初。恰與前錄相接。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b07"/>肇論略註</cell><cell>姚秦僧肇作</cell><cell>六卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>達摩未來以前。提倡宗乘者。肇公與竺道生二人而已。生公作論數篇。不傳於世。惜哉。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b12"/>寶藏論</cell><cell>姚秦僧肇作</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>此等寶藏。人人有之。一經指出。即能受用。爭奈窮子執迷不悟。可哀也已。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b16"/>六祖壇經</cell><cell>唐慧能大師說<p xml:id="pB28p0619b1611" cb:place="inline">門人記</p></cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>達摩西來。直指人心見性成佛。傳至六祖。其道大行。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b19"/>禪源諸詮集</cell><cell>唐宗密述</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>融通宗教。會成一味。此其序也。全書久亡。求之東瀛。亦不可得矣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0619b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0620a" n="0620a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a03"/>宗鏡錄</cell><cell>宋延壽述</cell><cell>百卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>以一心為宗。照萬法如鏡。凡各家互相是非者。皆以深理通之。誠圓融無礙法門也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a08"/>萬善同歸集</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>三卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>一心具萬善。萬善歸一心。不滯有為。不住無為。行菩薩道之正軌也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a12"/>心賦註</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>心無形相。而可賦乎。既賦矣。而又註之。誠描寫虛空之妙手也。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a16"/>高峰語錄</cell><cell>元原妙撰</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>直截根源。脫落窠臼。最足激發參學人志氣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620a19"/>中峰廣錄</cell><cell>元明本撰</cell><cell>三十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>刊華就實。因事明理。其間煅煉之穩密。勘辨之明確。無假借。無回護。凜凜然烈日嚴霜。誠宗門之巨擘也。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0620a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0620b" n="0620b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b05"/>天台宗</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b06"/>大乘止觀釋要</cell><cell>陳慧思述<p xml:id="pB28p0620b0611" cb:place="inline">明智旭釋</p></cell><cell>六卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>詳明三番止觀。皆先觀而後止。大師自證之法也。唯引起信論能生一切世間出世間善因果故之言。於善下添一惡字。蓮池大師辯之詳矣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b14"/>釋禪波羅密</cell><cell>隋智顗說<p xml:id="pB28p0620b1410" cb:place="inline">弟子法慎記</p></cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>長沙上林寺</cell><cell>廣明各種坐禪法門。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b17"/>小止觀</cell><cell>隋智顗述</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>杭州慧空經房</cell><cell>欲學坐禪。此法最為切近。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b19"/>天台四教儀集註</cell><cell>元蒙潤集</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>學天台教觀者。以此為圭臬。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0620b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0621a" n="0621a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a01"/>教觀綱宗</cell><cell>明智旭述</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>簡要不繁。最便初學。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0621a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a03"/>傳記</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a04"/>釋迦如來應化事蹟</cell><cell>國朝永珊集</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>採集各經。繪圖二百八幅。大致依如來成道記。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a07"/>高僧傳初集</cell><cell>梁慧皎撰</cell><cell>十四卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>自漢迄梁。正傳二百五十七人。附見二百三十九人。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a10"/>高僧傳二集</cell><cell>唐道宣撰</cell><cell>四十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>自梁迄唐。正傳三百三十一人。附見一百六十人。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a13"/>高僧傳三集</cell><cell>宋贊寧撰</cell><cell>三十卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>自唐迄宋。正傳五百三十人。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a15"/>禪林僧寶傳</cell><cell>宋惠洪撰</cell><cell>三十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>取宋代宗門之傑出者。八十有一人。各為傳而繫之以贊。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a19"/>比丘尼傳</cell><cell>梁寶唱撰</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>自晉迄梁。凡六十五人。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621a20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0621b" n="0621b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b01"/>居士傳</cell><cell>國朝彭際清述</cell><cell>五十六卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>自漢以來。正傳。二百二十七人。附見七十九人。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b04"/>善女人傳</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>自晉以來。正傳一百三十八人。附見九人。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0621b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b07"/>雜集</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b08"/>龍藏目錄</cell><cell>乾隆三年定</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>統計七百二十四函。七千二百四十卷。十五萬三千三百七十四紙。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b12"/>閱藏知津</cell><cell>明智旭輯</cell><cell>四十四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>分別部類先後次序。與藏本不同。每部之下。但載品中事理大概。使人自知綱要。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b17"/>法苑珠林</cell><cell>唐道世撰</cell><cell>百卷</cell><cell>常熟小石山房</cell><cell>以佛經故實。分類編排。凡一百篇。大旨推明罪福之由。以生人敬信之念。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0621b20"/>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0622a" n="0622a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a01"/>翻譯名義集</cell><cell>宋法雲編</cell><cell>二十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>內分六十四類。以梵語譯華言。並釋其義。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a04"/>教乘法數</cell><cell>雍正十三年重訂</cell><cell>十二卷</cell><cell>杭州慧空經房</cell><cell>從一數至八萬四千。備列教中名相。俾學者易於尋討。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a06"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a07"/>慈悲道場懺法<note place="inline">俗名梁皇懺</note></cell><cell>梁誌公寶唱等集</cell><cell>十卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>內分四十品。禮懺法門。此為最古。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a09"/>禪門日誦</cell><cell>寧波天童寺增輯</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>早晚課誦為僧家所必需。此外有可刪者存之。以順俗也。後附十宗略說。用開初學知見耳。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a11"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a13"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a14"/>弘明集</cell><cell>梁僧祐撰</cell><cell>十四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>薈萃漢魏六朝高僧名士辯論三寶之作。文既遒雅。義亦切要。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a17"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a18"/>鐔津文集</cell><cell>宋契嵩撰</cell><cell>二十卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>內多護教之言。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622a20"/>續原教論</cell><cell>明沈士榮著</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>辯論宋儒謗佛之言。最為透徹。</cell></row><row><cell>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0622b" n="0622b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b02"/>雲棲法彙</cell><cell>明袾宏述</cell><cell></cell><cell>同</cell><cell>內分三類。一釋經。二輯古。三手著。門人裒集大師遺書。盡於此矣。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b03"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b04"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b05"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b06"/>夢遊集</cell><cell>明德清著</cell><cell>五十五卷</cell><cell>揚州藏經院</cell><cell>憨山老人著作甚多。解釋經論數百卷。各別流行。門人搜其遺稿。彙成此集。</cell></row><row><cell cols="5">
<lb ed="B" n="0622b07"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b08"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b09"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b10"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b11"/>道家<note place="inline">與佛法相通者附錄於此</note></cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b13"/>老子翼</cell><cell>明焦竤輯</cell><cell>八卷</cell><cell>金陵刻經處</cell><cell>採輯古註六十四家。增以自作筆乘為解老者最為詳備之書。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b14"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b15"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b16"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b17"/>道德經解</cell><cell>明德清著</cell><cell>二卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>憨山此解。歷十五年而成。句斟字酌。極臻玄妙。</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b18"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0622b20"/>莊子內篇註</cell><cell>明德清著</cell><cell>四卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>莊子三十三篇。以內七篇為精要。故憨山註之。</cell></row><row><cell>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B28.0157.0623a" n="0623a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0623a01"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0623a02"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0623a03"/>陰符經發隱</cell><cell>石埭楊文會註</cell><cell>一卷</cell><cell>同</cell><cell>以佛法解釋。與舊註迥不相同。</cell></row></table>
